high_descs: Go forward to the sink, turn right after passing the island, turn right near the end of the island, then face the island.
Take the knife behind the bottle on the island.
Turn left, go forward a step, turn left to face the fridge, go to the fridge.
Cut the tomato in the fridge into slices.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the fridge.
Take a slice of tomato from the fridge.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink, take the tomato from the sink.
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the fridge.
Put the slice of tomato to the left of the rest of the tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of tomato in a fridge.

high_descs: Walk straight to the kitchen sink, then turn right and walk to the center of the kitchen island and turn to your right so that you are facing the pump bottle.
Pick up the knife, on the kitchen island, behind the pump bottle.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, cut the tomato on the top shelf into slices, and close the refrigerator door.
Turn to your left and walk straight, then turn to your right when you reach the kitchen sink.
Place the knife in the sink, in front of the green and yellow sponge.
Turn to your right and walk back to the refrigerator.
Pick up a slice of the tomato, on the top shelf and remove it from the refrigerator.
Turn left and go back to the sink on your right.
Place the tomato slice in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the tomato off, and remove the tomato from the sink.
Turn to your right and walk back to the refrigerator.
Place the tomato slice in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, to the left of the rest of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: go towards the sink, then right then face the island with utensils and a spray bottle on it
pick up the knife with the yellow handle
go toward the left and stop at the fridge
open the fridge and cut a slice of tomato
go to your left and stop at the sink
place the yellow handled knife into the sink
go back to your right to the fridge and open the door
remove the tomato slice from the fridge
shut the fridge door and then go back to the sink to your left
place the tomato in the sink and rinse it off
pick up the rinsed tomato and carry it back to the fridge
place the slice in the fridge next to the rest of the tomato
anns.task_desc: Place a cut, rinsed slice of tomato back into the fridge
